author: Katherine Rodriguez
title: Cincinnati Buildings to Light Up Blue for Coronavirus Frontline Workers
description: Cincinnati, Ohio, is lighting up blue on Thursday evening to support health care workers and essential employees during the coronavirus pandemic.
